# Slow Cooker Lentil Curry

Adapted from the overly mild [https://www.thekitchn.com/slow-cooker-lentil-curry-26195/...](https://www.thekitchn.com/slow-cooker-lentil-curry-261956) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251123030001/https://www.thekitchn.com/slow-cooker-lentil-curry-261956))

